<L>__{exterior forest late day}
<A>__{tamara watches conan from a distance. he silently stalks prey with nothing more than a knife.}
<B>__{a boar}
<A>__{its ears listen intently, aware. suddenly, it bolts.}
<B>__{conan}
<A>__{is just as quick, racing through the forest on a intercepting course with the great beast. he leaps over a fallen log, throwing his dagger with a sweep of his arm. the boar goes down, the blade through its jugular. conan walks up to the struggling beast, showing no satisfaction as he mercifully snaps its neck.}
